<abstract><t>This document provides a brief overview of Identity Enabled Networks (IDEAS) and discusses the need for a standardized network mapping system that is scalable, robust and flexible for future networks. This memo also identifies several key areas that should be investigated for the architecture design of these network mapping systems and their protocol interfaces.</t></abstract>

